{"tid":1527581,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"呼籲東涌車主發起發電機計劃 救救孩子","createTime":"2019-09-01T10:41:20.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-01T10:52:14.000Z","uid":72009,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"12442f140acc2b7c933ad5a8e24b4e5e22e6edb3","tid":1527581,"uid":72009,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-01T10:41:20.000Z","msg":"第二次世界大戰時在歐洲大陸執行的一次戰略性撤退。德國軍隊瓦解法國馬奇諾防線後包抄英法盟軍，盟軍撤至鄧寇克（法國北部靠近比利時的港口）後，為了避免被德軍圍殲，執行了當時最大規模的撤退行動，名為「發電機行動」。撤退過程中，英國皇家空軍與德國空軍爆發了激烈的空戰，最終英國仍得以動員各種大小船隻，將大部份的士兵撤離歐洲大陸。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />時間無多，快"},{"pid":"b0ef19f5925accb3a0187f213a6bd20c20e5bd28","tid":1527581,"uid":127929,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-01T10:52:12.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">[緊急] 各位 東涌 青衣 街坊請立即落街接放學</span></span>"},{"pid":"1fc34c62a1bb0f5b61c8f232ea7fa023324cc85e","tid":1527581,"uid":44358,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-01T10:52:14.000Z","msg":"有車就接送，冇車就開放屋企收留<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}